README for the LaTeX package epl2
---------------------------------



DESCRIPTION
-----------

This is a LaTeX package designed for the production of papers
to appear in the European journal "EPL".


FILES
-----

    epl2.cls            set of LaTeX macros specifically designed
                        to produce a paper in EPL style.

    epl-template.tex    example of an article
    epl-template.eps    example of a figure (used by epl-template.tex)


    eplbib.bst          BiBTeX style file

INSTALLATION
------------

To start writing your paper

    *) put epl2.cls and epl-template.tex in a working directory
    *) rename epl-template.tex to a name of your choise (here we
       assume "mypaper.tex")
    *) edit mypaper.tex


